A game wrriten for unity and windows , it necesitates the existance of Unity and Blender for models
The unique scene is written in C3, the background image is taken from internet
The game has 2 Players but no definit winner, the game ends when you press enter.
The ball direction,initial position and the force the ball is trown to the pins.
The inital position on x axis is controlled using the arrows:left and right.
To control the force and speed you use arrows: up and down
to control the angle you trow the ball indicated by the purple arrow use buttobs: A and S
To change player use button:B
To restart game use button:R

